data.description: GREAT POOL!   Enjoy your private pool, a home with four bedrooms AND private office.  A David Weekley re-sale.  No carpet in the home, the kitchen and living area are open and large.    Granite counter tops and a lovely gas range, make cooking fun!  From the kitchen, you have a view of the home and pool area. Come see this home today.  Enjoy the private pool.
